---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/ui/CTASection.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/ui/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import TestimonialsSection from '../../components/sections/TestimonialsSection.astro';

const city = "Ridgewood";
const title = "CPA in Ridgewood NJ | Tax & Accounting Services | ProAxis";
const description = "ProAxis provides expert CPA services in Ridgewood NJ — high-net-worth tax planning, executive compensation, trust & estate planning, and medical practice accounting. 100% virtual.";
const canonical = "/service-areas/ridgewood/";
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas/" },
  { name: city }
];
const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": ["LocalBusiness", "AccountingService"],
  "name": "ProAxis Tax & Accounting Services",
  "telephone": "+12018002330",
  "email": "info@proaxiscpa.com",
  "url": "https://proaxiscpa.com",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Hasbrouck Heights",
    "addressRegion": "NJ",
    "postalCode": "07604",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Ridgewood, NJ" }
};
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonical} {schema} {breadcrumbs}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1C1C1E 0%, #2E75B6 100%);" class="py-14 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-4" style="background-color: rgba(197,165,90,0.2); color: #C5A55A;">
        Serving {city}, NJ &bull; 100% Virtual
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading text-white mb-4">CPA &amp; Accounting Services in {city}, NJ</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">ProAxis delivers expert tax preparation, tax planning, bookkeeping, and business advisory to {city} businesses and residents — all virtually, all on your schedule.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white" style="background-color: #22C55E;">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/40">Call (201) 800-2330</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 lg:py-16">

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Ridgewood's Business &amp; Community Landscape</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Ridgewood is consistently ranked among Bergen County's — and New Jersey's — most desirable communities. Its picturesque downtown village centered on Ridgewood Avenue offers an uncommonly charming mix of independent retailers, acclaimed restaurants, professional offices, and community gathering spaces that have helped Ridgewood maintain a distinct small-town identity despite its location just 25 miles from midtown Manhattan. The village's tree-lined streets, Victorian architecture, and top-rated school system have made it a perennial destination for families relocating from New York City in search of exceptional public schools and a more residential pace of life — without entirely sacrificing urban convenience.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The professional composition of Ridgewood's resident population is striking. The village has an outsized concentration of attorneys, physicians, executives, financial professionals, and business owners relative to its size. Many residents commute to Manhattan via NJ Transit's Pascack Valley Line, which connects Ridgewood to Hoboken and New York Penn Station, or by car via Route 17. The incomes these professionals earn — frequently including not just salaries but also annual bonuses, equity compensation, deferred compensation arrangements, and investment income — create tax situations of substantial complexity that demand year-round planning rather than last-minute annual filing.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Ridgewood's real estate market reflects the community's affluence. Median home prices in Ridgewood are among the highest in Bergen County, and property tax bills that can reach $20,000 to $30,000 annually are common in the village's more desirable neighborhoods. These property tax levels, combined with NJ state income taxes on six-figure earnings, mean that virtually every Ridgewood homeowner who itemizes deductions has long since exceeded the federal $10,000 SALT cap — and is effectively subsidizing the U.S. Treasury rather than deducting the full cost of living in New Jersey. Understanding the available workarounds — particularly the NJ BAIT election for business owners — is essential for Ridgewood tax clients.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The downtown Ridgewood business district on Ridgewood Avenue is home to a sophisticated array of independent businesses: boutique clothing and gift shops, wine and spirits retailers, interior designers, hair salons, specialty food purveyors, and a strong concentration of professional service firms including law offices, financial advisory practices, and medical specialty groups. These businesses require professional bookkeeping systems, proper NJ sales tax compliance, and thoughtful entity structuring — many are structured as LLCs or S-Corps and would benefit from a CPA who proactively identifies planning opportunities rather than just processing transactions.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">Medical professionals are a particularly significant segment of the Ridgewood client base. Ridgewood has a substantial number of physicians in private practice, either operating solo practices or as part of small group practices. The financial management of a medical practice — from overhead cost tracking to physician compensation modeling to retirement plan selection — requires specialized expertise. Defined benefit plans, for example, can allow high-earning physicians in their peak earning years to shelter significantly more income from taxation than a standard SEP-IRA or Solo 401(k), but they require careful actuarial and tax planning to implement correctly.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Tax &amp; Accounting Needs in Ridgewood</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Ridgewood's high-income, professionally sophisticated resident base creates a set of planning needs that go well beyond standard tax preparation:</p>
    <ul class="list-none space-y-3 mb-6">
      {[
        { heading: "Executive compensation planning", text: "Stock options (ISOs and NQSOs), restricted stock units (RSUs), deferred compensation plans (including 409A-compliant arrangements), and annual bonus timing — each with its own NJ and federal tax treatment that requires careful modeling." },
        { heading: "NYC commuter tax optimization", text: "Many Ridgewood residents work in Manhattan. Proper coordination of NJ and NY state returns, work-from-home day allocation, and the application of the NJ credit for taxes paid to NY can have meaningful dollar impact." },
        { heading: "Trust and estate planning coordination", text: "Ridgewood's high-net-worth population needs CPAs who can coordinate with their estate attorneys on trust accounting, gift tax filings, and estate plan implementation. The federal estate tax exemption sunset anticipated after 2025 makes this planning particularly time-sensitive." },
        { heading: "Investment portfolio tax strategy", text: "Tax-loss harvesting, qualified dividend income optimization, municipal bond allocation decisions, and the management of concentrated stock positions — particularly relevant for Ridgewood's investment-savvy resident community." },
        { heading: "Medical practice accounting", text: "Physician compensation structures, practice overhead analysis, medical equipment depreciation, retirement plan selection, and eventual practice valuation or sale planning." },
      ].map((item) => (
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #C5A55A;"></div>
          <div><span class="font-semibold" style="color: #1C1C1E;">{item.heading}:</span> <span class="text-gray-700">{item.text}</span></div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <!-- ProAxis Services -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">ProAxis Serves Ridgewood Businesses &amp; Residents</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-5">High-net-worth tax planning, executive compensation analysis, medical practice accounting — ProAxis brings the depth of expertise Ridgewood's community demands, delivered through a convenient virtual model.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {[
          { name: "Tax Preparation", link: "/tax-services/tax-preparation/" },
          { name: "Tax Planning", link: "/tax-services/tax-planning/" },
          { name: "Bookkeeping", link: "/business-services/bookkeeping/" },
          { name: "Business Advisory", link: "/business-services/" },
          { name: "NJ SALT Consulting", link: "/tax-services/nj-salt-consulting/" },
          { name: "Fractional CFO", link: "/business-services/fractional-cfo/" },
        ].map((svc) => (
          <a href={svc.link} class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 font-medium transition-all" style="color: #2E75B6;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
            {svc.name}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Why Choose a Virtual CPA in Ridgewood</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Ridgewood residents are busy — managing demanding careers, raising families, and maintaining active community lives. The traditional CPA model of in-person appointments and paper-driven processes simply doesn't fit the pace of a Ridgewood professional's life. ProAxis's virtual model puts a responsive, expert CPA team at your fingertips without requiring you to carve time out of a packed schedule.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">And because ProAxis is headquartered right here in Bergen County, we understand Ridgewood's specific context — the NJ property tax situation, the typical commuter tax issues, the kinds of equity compensation packages that come from the Wall Street and corporate law firm employers that many Ridgewood residents work for — in a way that a distant national firm simply cannot.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Nearby Areas We Also Serve</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
      {[
        { name: "Paramus", slug: "paramus" },
        { name: "Fair Lawn", slug: "fair-lawn" },
        { name: "Hackensack", slug: "hackensack" },
        { name: "Bergen County (all)", slug: "bergen-county" },
      ].map((area) => (
        <a href={`/service-areas/${area.slug}/`} class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border hover:shadow-sm transition-all" style="border-color: #2E75B6; color: #2E75B6; background-color: rgba(46,117,182,0.05);">{area.name}</a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Ready to get started? <a href="/contact/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">Schedule a free consultation</a> with ProAxis, or explore our <a href="/tax-services/tax-planning/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">tax planning services</a> and <a href="/business-services/bookkeeping/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">bookkeeping solutions</a>.</p>
  </article>

  <TestimonialsSection />
  <CTASection heading={"CPA Services in " + city + ", NJ — Schedule Your Free Consultation"} />
</BaseLayout>
